The <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver" title="The MutationObserver interface provides the ability to watch for changes being made to the DOM tree. It is designed as a replacement for the older Mutation Events feature which was part of the DOM3 Events specification."><code>MutationObserver</code></a> interface provides the ability to watch for changes being made to the <a href="/en-US/docs/DOM">DOM</a> tree. It is designed as a replacement for the older <a href="/en-US/docs/DOM/Mutation_events">Mutation Events</a> feature which was part of the DOM3 Events specification.